Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.36,0:02:19.64,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}飽きるくらい　全部キミがほしいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.76,0:02:21.95,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}ハートは涙でいっぱい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.47,0:02:26.77,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}恋のいろはとかまだわかってないんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.71,0:02:30.22,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}何度も繰り返すけど
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.27,0:02:32.54,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}寸前でまた次回へ　
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.01,0:02:38.77,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}スイートな乙女心は　あいにく取り扱ってないのです
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.00,0:02:41.56,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}ねぇ　これがI LOVE YOU
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.61,0:02:45.52,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Someday I really really send it, precious for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.49,0:02:50.66,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Someday I really really send it, precious for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.61,0:02:45.52,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Someday I really really send it, precious for you!
